tip.text: A simple yet great place for socializing with tasty food. The mix of Mediterranean dishes is simply a pleasure. Borata, short rips, lobster bun, black rice, sorbet and cream brûlée
French toast, healthy fruits with cottage cheese, house club sandwich, eggs Benedict, and the tea.
An outstanding Italian place, the balanced taste with perfect cooking and amazing staff make the experience worth it. Go for Gorgonzola salad, Branzino, Linguini Di Mari and finish with tiramisu
Food, staff and ambiance are amazing. We had fun with the remarkable and friendly staff, cant wait to be there again!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
